title: Creature Feature
description: Craig finds himself being chased by a monster in the Creek that's straight out of the movies!

title: Council of the Creek: Operation Hive-Mind
description: Hive Mind - When bees take over the Trading Tree, Craig must assemble the Council of the Creek to avert disaster.

title: The Ice Pop Trio
description: Craig sets out in search of Ice Pops on a hot day with the help of an unlikely duo.

title: Kelsey Quest
description: Kelsey accepts a quest from the Elders of the Creek, but is she ready for her terrifying opponent?

title: Beyond the Rapids
description: Resident creek scientist Wren enlists Craig to voyage through dangerous waters in search of a path to the Ocean.

title: Into the Overpast
description: Craig and The Green Poncho travel to the Other Side of the Creek where Craig learns Green Poncho's shocking origin story.

title: The Brood
description: Craig's determination to get his granddad a cicada shell causes him, Kelsey and JP to become trapped in their stump!

title: The Sunflower
description: Our Trio makes a new friend in the Creek, but when her pet befalls a tragic fate, Kelsey believes she knows how to help.

title: Craig of the Car
description: Craig gets to be the ultimate backseat driver.

title: How Was Your Day?
description: Craig and his friends run afoul of the rock kids.

title: New Jersey
description: After donning a brand new Jersey, JP is recruited by the Hockey Kids! The only way to get JP back is for Craig and Kelsey to hit the ice!

title: Ferret Quest
description: The kids are on the search for an elusive ferret in the Creek.  Kelsey unites her friends Stacks and Wildernessa to find it, but worries they'd rather hangout with each other instead of her.

title: Craig of the Beach
description: Craig gets to hit the beach with his friends and family, but starts to get worried his Dad is more fun than him.

title: Plush Kingdom
description: Craig, Kelsey, JP and Jessica discover a group of plushie obsessed kids, deep within the creek.

title: JPony
description: JP decides to follow his heart and tries to join the Horse Girls.

title: King of Camping
description: The Williams Family goes camping and Craig helps his dad prove he's the King of Camping.

title: Craig World
description: Craig creates an amusement park in the Creek! But when things start to get stale, he vows to make it bigger and better, no matter what it takes!

title: The Rise and Fall of the Green Poncho
description: Craig tries to warn his friends about the Other Side of the Creek with a tale from the Creek's defender - the Green Poncho.

title: Pencil Break Mania
description: When Pencil Break Mania hits the Creek, JP finds himself as an unlikely champion and is forced to defend his title against the very best!

title: Winter Creeklympics
description: Craig, Kelsey and JP try their luck at winning Gold in their first ever, Winter Creeklympics!

title: Afterschool Snackdown
description: Craig enters a food competition in the Creek but worries he may be out of his league.

title: Breaking the Ice
description: While searching a once unreachable part of the Creek, Craig gets stranded with his longtime rival, Wildernessa!

title: Kelsey the Author
description: Craig and Stacks help Kelsey become a real author turning her story into a book!

title: The Bike Thief
description: Craig investigates the theft of the 10 Speed's bikes in hopes of finding the culprit!

title: Memories of Bobby
description: When a pillar of the Creek community leaves, our trio mourns their loss by remembering the good times.

title: The Ground Is Lava!
description: When an intense game of "The Ground is Lava" breaks out, Craig must carefully traverse the Creek to save his sister.

title: Winter Break
description: Craig returns to the Creek after the long Winter Break only to find an empty wasteland and danger lurking in the snow.

title: Welcome to Creek Street
description: Craig and his friends create their own neighborhood in the snow!

title: I Don't Need a Hat
description: Craig decides to ditch his hat on a chilly day and it becomes a battle for body heat.

title: Alternate Creekiverse
description: Craig, Kelsey and JP imagine a disturbing alternate reality where they never became friends!

title: Snow Day
description: Craig and his friends desperately want a Snow Day, so they turn to the most powerful people they know... The Witches of the Creek!

title: The Williams Family Opening Theme Song
description: Craig imagines what it would be like if his family had a TV Show.

title: Sunday Clothes
description: JP dirties his last clean clothes and he must wear his Sunday best to the creek.

title: Lost in the Sewer
description: Craig agrees to help The Sewer Queen map the sewers, but he quickly finds himself in over his head.

title: Kelsey the Elder
description: A spat between the Elders of the Creek leaves an opening in their tabletop role playing game, so Kelsey joins the campaign!

title: The Other Side: The Tournament
description: The Tournament - Hoping to win a special prize for his Dad's birthday, Craig and his friends compete in a tournament on the Other Side of the Creek!

title: Jacob of the Creek
description: A terrible haircut forces Craig to go undercover at the Creek.

title: Cats of the Creek
description: A trio of cats, led by a young kitten named Craig, seek adventures in the untamed wilderness of creek. Meanwhile, a team of crime-fighting superhero felines curl up in their Pounce City headquarters. Only on Cat-toon Network!

title: Fan or Foe
description: When Elder Con comes to the Creek, Craig, Kelsey and JP each have a con experience they'll never forget.

title: Council of the Creek
description: The circle game wreaks havoc on the Creek, so Craig forms a council to restore order.

title: The Last Game of Summer
description: It's the last day of summer, and the last chance for Craig to uncover an ancient treasure beneath the Creek.

title: Snow Place Like Home
description: While taking refuge from the chilly Creek, Craig and his friends decide to hangout at his house until lunch time!

title: Fall Anthology
description: In an attempt to finish a school project, Craig remembers some of his favorite Fall moments.

title: Trick or Creek
description: It's Halloween at the Creek, and Craig is on a mission to collect as much candy as humanly possible, but a spooky ghoul from the Creek's past threatens his haul.
